<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 16:10:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>外国记者协会呼吁以色列取消对加沙独立媒体的禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/foreign-press-association-calls-on-israel-to-lift-ban-on-independent-press-in-gaza/0000018e-be21-d92b-adaf-fe6513ea0000</link><description>FPA董事会表示，是否前往加沙实地的决定应由每个国际媒体自行决定，全面禁令限制了世界目睹战争给各方带来的真正代价的能力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/foreign-press-association-calls-on-israel-to-lift-ban-on-independent-press-in-gaza/0000018e-be21-d92b-adaf-fe6513ea0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日加沙战争六周年纪念日，全球各地举行集会和抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/rallies-protests-held-across-the-globe-on-six-month-anniversary-of-oct-7-war-in-gaza/0000018e-bdcb-db65-a7af-fdcba4940000</link><description>周日，前人质、人质家属和领导人向挤满的人群发表讲话，这是 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以色列已有半年的日子</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:03:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/rallies-protests-held-across-the-globe-on-six-month-anniversary-of-oct-7-war-in-gaza/0000018e-bdcb-db65-a7af-fdcba4940000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔任命新警察局长，因滥用职权和违反信任而受到调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-picks-new-police-chief-who-was-investigated-for-abusing-powers-breach-of-trust/0000018e-be20-d6f4-afaf-be62f23a0000</link><description>2015年，时任警察局长阿尔谢奇拒绝了内部调查部门拒绝阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德晋升的建议。警方消息人士称佩莱德为“本-格维尔的傀儡”，两人的关系可以追溯到十多年前</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:44:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-picks-new-police-chief-who-was-investigated-for-abusing-powers-breach-of-trust/0000018e-be20-d6f4-afaf-be62f23a0000</guid></item><item><title>备受争议的影响力活动背后的官员被任命为内塔尼亚胡的军事部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-new-military-secretary-is-an-officer-who-used-a-minor-for-unauthorized-psy-ops/0000018e-bde4-d753-a7ee-ffe7657c0000</link><description>双桅船。总理任命的罗曼·戈夫曼 (Roman Gofman) 将军批准向一名 17 岁的年轻人发送机密材料，要求他在网上发布这些材料。该少年随后被指控从事间谍活动，并被关押了 18 个月，直到以色列国防军称他为军事情报部门工作并将他释放。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:19:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-new-military-secretary-is-an-officer-who-used-a-minor-for-unauthorized-psy-ops/0000018e-bde4-d753-a7ee-ffe7657c0000</guid></item><item><title>被指控在特拉维夫碾压抗议者的司机将被释放并软禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/driver-accused-of-running-over-protesters-in-tel-aviv-to-be-released-to-house-arrest/0000018e-bdbc-d871-ad9e-fffe33850000</link><description>法院表示，有合理的理由相信海姆·西洛特金犯下了这一罪行，但可能需要相当长的时间来审查他对事件的说法。警方要求推迟一天释放，以便他们可以就这一决定提出上诉</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 13:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/driver-accused-of-running-over-protesters-in-tel-aviv-to-be-released-to-house-arrest/0000018e-bdbc-d871-ad9e-fffe33850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军消息来源证实真主党首次击落先进的 Hermes 900 无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-in-a-first-hezbollah-shoots-down-advanced-hermes-900-uav/0000018e-bd86-d92b-adaf-ffe63fde0000</link><description>Hermes 900 是一款多用途无人机，飞行时间为 36 小时。它的两架前身 Hermes 450 过去曾遭到袭击，但周六的拦截事件代价高昂，提醒人们以色列国防军无人机并非无懈可击</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 12:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-in-a-first-hezbollah-shoots-down-advanced-hermes-900-uav/0000018e-bd86-d92b-adaf-ffe63fde0000</guid></item><item><title>在所有施压策略都用尽的情况下，以色列和哈马斯现在必须谈判达成真正的加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/all-pressure-tactics-exhausted-israel-and-hamas-must-now-negotiate-a-real-gaza-deal/0000018e-bd08-dfde-a3ef-bf7bbc180000</link><description>如果迄今为止，以色列的政策依赖于调解者的外交努力及其自身的军事力量，那么谈判现在取决于美国政府和以色列公众压力 — — 及其对总理可能构成的政治威胁</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/all-pressure-tactics-exhausted-israel-and-hamas-must-now-negotiate-a-real-gaza-deal/0000018e-bd08-dfde-a3ef-bf7bbc180000</guid></item><item><title>世界法院就指控德国在加沙战争中援助以色列的案件举行听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/world-court-opens-hearings-in-a-case-accusing-germany-of-aiding-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018e-bd28-df12-afaf-bfad44f30000</link><description>尼加拉瓜向国际法院请愿，称通过向以色列提供政治、财政和军事支持以及取消对近东救济工程处的资助，“德国正在为种族灭绝的实施提供便利”，并寻求结束德国对以色列的军事和其他援助</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:45:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/world-court-opens-hearings-in-a-case-accusing-germany-of-aiding-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018e-bd28-df12-afaf-bfad44f30000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：随着加沙战争进入六个月大关，内塔尼亚胡失去了议会多数席位；甘茨保持领先</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/polls-netanyahu-loses-knesset-majority-as-gaza-war-hits-six-month-mark-gantz-stays-ahead/0000018e-bd00-dbdb-adaf-bfe55e700000</link><description>两项调查均显示甘茨领导的政党以 32-30 个席位领先，内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团以 21-19 个席位紧随其后。两项民意调查均未显示财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇的宗教犹太复国主义跨过选举门槛</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/polls-netanyahu-loses-knesset-majority-as-gaza-war-hits-six-month-mark-gantz-stays-ahead/0000018e-bd00-dbdb-adaf-bfe55e700000</guid></item><item><title>发表以色列作家共存文章的格尔尼卡编辑辞职，称她不同意撤稿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/guernica-editor-who-published-israeli-writers-coexistence-essay-resigns/0000018e-bce5-df26-a99e-fcff51e00000</link><description>“该杂志坚持撤回该作品； 《格尔尼卡》杂志主编吉娜·摩尔 (Jina Moore) 写道：“我不这么认为。”在《格尔尼卡》撤回英裔以色列作家兼翻译家乔安娜·陈 (Joanna Chen) 的文章一个月后，她宣布辞职。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/guernica-editor-who-published-israeli-writers-coexistence-essay-resigns/0000018e-bce5-df26-a99e-fcff51e00000</guid></item><item><title>亲爱的拜登总统，您同意以色列定居者使用美国武器吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/fyi-joe-biden-israels-settlers-use-american-weapons/0000018e-b82b-d906-a5cf-babfb7800000</link><description>这些武器正被一个与军队类似的恐吓、恐怖和掠夺政权所使用，该政权是由国家公民及其代理人在西岸建立的政权</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/fyi-joe-biden-israels-settlers-use-american-weapons/0000018e-b82b-d906-a5cf-babfb7800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电视台会遭遇与俄罗斯电视台同样的命运吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/will-israeli-television-suffer-the-same-fate-as-russia/0000018e-b8b6-db6c-a9ee-fcb6ace40000</link><description>在系列狂热历史上，这是第一次没有以色列节目参加今年的主要节日 - 考虑到加沙战争的状况，以色列制作人不应感到惊讶。这并不意味着以色列在边缘地区没有强大的存在</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 07:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/will-israeli-television-suffer-the-same-fate-as-russia/0000018e-b8b6-db6c-a9ee-fcb6ace40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队从加沙南部撤军，但没有实现其主要目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/one-step-away-from-victory-as-israels-soldiers-march-out-of-southern-gaza-really/0000018e-b9ef-df26-a99e-f9ffd03f0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理所追求的胜利并不像他所描述的那么接近：以色列国防军士兵正在离开加沙南部，以色列离实现战争目标并不远，现在必须应对西方更多的反对</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 03:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/one-step-away-from-victory-as-israels-soldiers-march-out-of-southern-gaza-really/0000018e-b9ef-df26-a99e-f9ffd03f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：我们正处于释放加沙人质的正确时机，“我们将承担代价”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article-live/report-israel-hamas-making-progress-toward-hostage-deal-after-cairo-negotiations/0000018e-bb73-df26-a99e-fb7f5b100000</link><description>外国外交官表示，埃及关于加沙谈判进展的报道中存在“谨慎乐观” ■ 哈马斯否认谈判取得进展，称以色列“拒绝了一切要求” ■ 以色列国防军称其杀害了真主党精锐拉德万部队的高级指挥官 ■ 真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉称大马士革的袭击是“直接攻击伊朗”</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 02:54:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article-live/report-israel-hamas-making-progress-toward-hostage-deal-after-cairo-negotiations/0000018e-bb73-df26-a99e-fb7f5b100000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件已过去六个月，数千人集会要求人质返回</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/thousands-rally-for-hostages-return-on-six-month-mark-of-oct-7-hamas-attack/0000018e-b9e5-d712-a3df-f9ef96970000</link><description>该活动由人质和失踪家庭论坛组织，该论坛解释说，在耶路撒冷举行集会源于希望靠近决策地点，旨在提高不住在特拉维夫的以色列人的认识</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 20:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/thousands-rally-for-hostages-return-on-six-month-mark-of-oct-7-hamas-attack/0000018e-b9e5-d712-a3df-f9ef96970000</guid></item><item><title>美国预计将提出新的人质交易提案；以色列官员不确定哈马斯会放松立场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-to-propose-new-hostage-deal-israeli-officials-unsure-hamas-will-ease-position/0000018e-b9f9-d7ee-a39e-fdff2d210000</link><description>美国政府正在利用其影响力向哈马斯和以色列施加压力，因为他们在谈判中的红线问题上仍存在争执。以色列代表团周日一直在开罗进行会谈</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 20:39:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-to-propose-new-hostage-deal-israeli-officials-unsure-hamas-will-ease-position/0000018e-b9f9-d7ee-a39e-fdff2d210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军官员：汗尤尼斯撤军是行动需要，不是人质交易的姿态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-officials-khan-yunis-withdrawal-is-operational-need-not-gesture-for-hostage-deal/0000018e-b9f1-df26-a99e-f9ffa5800000</link><description>以色列军队早就明白，让军队驻扎在加沙会给他们带来危险，并希望他们的缺席会导致“另一方从其藏身之处现身”——即使面临以色列再次遭受火箭弹袭击的风险</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 20:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-officials-khan-yunis-withdrawal-is-operational-need-not-gesture-for-hostage-deal/0000018e-b9f1-df26-a99e-f9ffa5800000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列服役时间最长的巴勒斯坦安全囚犯死于癌症</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/longest-serving-palestinian-security-prisoner-in-israel-dies-from-cancer/0000018e-b9c9-df26-a99e-f9ffc1350000</link><description>瓦利德·达卡 (Walid Daka) 曾参与 1984 年杀害一名以色列国防军士兵的行动，自从被诊断出患有癌症后的两年内，他多次申请提前释放，但均遭到拒绝。他在以色列监狱服刑近40年，去世享年62岁</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 19:10:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/longest-serving-palestinian-security-prisoner-in-israel-dies-from-cancer/0000018e-b9c9-df26-a99e-f9ffc1350000</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳决定回购以色列餐厅的背后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/mcdonalds-israel-buyback-caving-to-boycott-or-business-sense/0000018e-b963-d712-a3df-f9eb591a0000</link><description>该连锁店表示，此举是其频繁洗牌加盟商的一部分，但批评人士表示，由于穆斯林世界的销售低迷，该公司向 BDS 抗议者让步了</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/mcdonalds-israel-buyback-caving-to-boycott-or-business-sense/0000018e-b963-d712-a3df-f9eb591a0000</guid></item><item><title>至少水獭正在返回以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/at-least-the-otters-are-returning-to-israels-north/0000018e-b985-db6c-a9ee-fd95a6980000</link><description>由于水资源减少和致命的道路交叉口而几乎灭绝后，对水獭粪便的调查显示，在高速公路下为它们建造的安全通道的帮助下，它们已经回到了以色列北部失踪的地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/at-least-the-otters-are-returning-to-israels-north/0000018e-b985-db6c-a9ee-fd95a6980000</guid></item></channel></rss>